data.description: Experience luxurious living in this spacious home on 4.45 acres nestled in a serene and picturesque neighborhood. This stunning property boasts four bedrooms, three bathrooms, and not just one but two offices, offering ample space for work and living. Inside, discover the charm of 10-foot ceilings complemented by elegant luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, creating an air of sophistication and modern appeal.  The kitchen, a blank slate, presents an opportunity for personalization and design, allowing you to create the culinary space of your dreams. Appreciate the grandeur of tray ceilings in both the living room and master bedroom, adding a touch of elegance to these central living spaces. While the master bathroom awaits the final touches of a renovation, the rest of the home gleams with potential and space. With generously sized bedrooms, a guest bedroom with an adjacent hallway bathroom, and the tranquil seclusion provided by the lush trees surrounding the property, privacy and comfort are guaranteed.  A spacious two-car garage offers plenty of storage space. The property’s positioning, set back from the road, provides a serene ambiance with added privacy. Come home to a perfect blend of ample space, privacy, and the potential to personalize your dream home. Ideal for buyers seeking a peaceful expansive property with room for personal touches.
